CGI/ToXML version 0.01
======================

CGI::ToXML is a module that allows the conversion of CGI objects to XML.
More details are available in the associated POD.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  CGI.pm  (Not directly, but for testing purposes)
  XML::Simple (For XML output)

